  "instructions": [
    "Heat sesame oil in a cast-iron pot over medium-high heat.",
    "Add Japanese rice and cook until lightly browned, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 18 minutes, or until water is absorbed.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together soy sauce, sushi vinegar, and sugar.",
    "Remove rice from heat and stir in soy sauce mixture, vanilla pod, ginger, and green onions.",
    "Cover pot and let rest for 5 minutes before serving."
